reviewText: Simple hilarious! Why did she have to end this series??? Loved all six seasons. This is probably the last season that still seemed like reality TV. The next two seasons are more scripted/staged and more about her celeb guests. Just as funny, just different format. At least she is still doing Bravo! stand up specials. Keep it up KG!
